<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1 >健康险</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="javascript:;" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=2618117" target="_blank" class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" nslog-type="90000102"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num"></span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">健康险，是健康保险的中文简称，是指保险公司通过疾病保险、医疗保险、失能收入损失保险和护理保险等方式对因健康原因导致的损失给付保险金的保险。</div><div class="para" label-module="para">与其相关法律有《健康保险管理办法》等。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div id="hotspotmining_s" class="clearfix" alog-alias="hotspotmining-subLemma-">
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="hotspotmining" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><ul class="hotspotminingNavbar clearfix">
<li class="active" data-id="457964">最新新闻</li>
</ul>
<div id="hotspotminingContent-457964" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" style="display: block">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-10/09/c_1125080525.htm?baike" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=e1071b60bc19ebc4c02d25d9e41bfcca/960a304e251f95ca49feb6b3c6177f3e670952af.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-10/09/c_1125080525.htm?baike" target="_blank">健康险成民生保障网重要支撑</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2019-10-09 09:10</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>近日，中国银保监会最新数据显示，今年前8个月健康保险继续保持快速增长势头，健康保险保费收入4991亿元，同比增长31.48%；健康保险赔付支出1430亿元，同比增长37.5%。从数据看，健康保险仍然是保险行业前8月数据中最亮眼的看点，也是所有险种中同比增长最快的业务。</span><a href="http://www.xinhuanet.com/fortune/2019-10/09/c_1125080525.htm?baike" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_rel ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_rel_tit">相关新闻</div>
<ul class="hotspotminingContent_rel_cnt">
</ul>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_web">内容来自<img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/logo_xinhuanet_6fe68e7.png"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
健康险
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">险种分类</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
医疗,疾病,收入保障,护理保险
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">主要起源</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
人身保险分支出来的一支独立险种
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">年&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;龄</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
3岁以上、60岁以下
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">相关法律</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95">健康保险管理办法</a>》
</dd>
</dl></div>
